data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat! This stunning property spans 27.42 acres, offering a perfect blend of comfort and nature. With 2024 sq ft, 4 beds, and 2 baths, this home exudes charm. A barn and equipment run-in storage cater to various hobbies. Dive into relaxation with a pool and hot tub. Nature lovers will adore the walking trails and abundant wildlife. This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Seize the chance to embrace tranquility on this expansive canvas. Your oasis awaits!
